Title: I Want to Breath Different Air
DateModified: '2019-02-19'
DatePublished: '2019-02-19'
Url: https://www.worldnomads.com/create/scholarships/writing/2019/applications/i-want-to-breath-different-air
SetInCountry: Portugal
Category: A leap into the unknown
AuthorName: Tara Szafarz
AuthorCountry: United Kingdom (Great Britain
Text: "Bored of life back home, being stuck in a stupid system really doesn\u2019\
  t tickle Sofi Doyle. Inquisitive and brave, this 20 year old adventurer is determined\
  \ to breath a \ndifferent air and finally see a new way of life. \n\nOn her journey\
  \ she makes brilliant new friends and rescues a loyal animal companion off the street,\
  \ who just so happened to save her life. \n\nFilled with adventure, emotion and\
  \ a fair share of plot twists this could possibly be the best story I will ever\
  \ write. Please let me make Sofi Doyle come alive so she can start her adventure!\
  \ Passion and friendship are to be expected but also a few heart wrenching moments."
